":3,"quote":{"pid":"f02b554cec9db16af4979291849e4eb979287745","tid":2512052,"uid":72994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:34:45.000Z","msg":"點backup youtube最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">推介一個免費同開源嘅 backup 短片工具俾大家：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/MrS0m30n3/youtube-dl-gui\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FMrS0m30n3%2Fyoutube-dl-gui&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=07033ccf\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/MrS0m30n3/youtube-dl-gui</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\">個網拉落去 Downloads 度揀返適合你嘅版本，<br />\n如 Windows 版就可以揀返 Windows Portable。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">下載同解壓縮後打開 youtube-dl-gui.exe，<br />\n係上面果格入 youtube link，<br />\n跟住揀下載位置 &gt; 撳 add 同右下角個 download 掣就得。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3k5XMzD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3k5XMzD.gif&h=ef08453b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果條 LINK 有 PLAYLIST id ，<br />\n會成個 PLAYLIST 下載。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">另外同樣能支援 facebook, vimeo 影片下載，<br />\n用法一樣。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXzd4mk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXzd4mk.gif&h=3e87e179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他短片網站支援 LIST：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ytdl-org.github.io/youtube-dl/supportedsites.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fytdl-org.github.io%2Fyoutube-dl%2Fsupportedsites.html&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=057717b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://ytdl-org.github.io/youtube-dl/supportedsites.html</a>"},{"pid":"7f86a71cb0e9d9ecfb7a7a3049d4bfcaf70ef45b","tid":2512052,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse